====================================================
SESSION 24: PROXYCHAINS CONFIGURATION REVIEW
====================================================

FILE REVIEWED:
    /etc/proxychains4.conf

PROXY MODES OBSERVED:
    - dynamic_chain
    - strict_chain
    - round_robin_chain
    - random_chain

DNS SETTINGS:
    proxy_dns
    proxy_dns_old
    proxy_dns_daemon 127.0.0.1:1053

REMOTE DNS SUBNET:
    remote_dns_subnet 224

TIMEOUT SETTINGS:
    tcp_read_time_out 15000
    tcp_connect_time_out 8000

LOCAL NETWORK EXCLUSIONS:
    localnet 10.0.0.0/255.0.0.0
    localnet 172.16.0.0/255.240.0.0
    localnet 192.168.0.0/255.255.0.0

PROXY TYPES SUPPORTED:
    - http
    - socks4
    - socks5
    - raw

PROXY LIST CONFIGURATION:
    socks4 127.0.0.1 1080

NOTES:
    Proxychains was configured to support tunneling traffic
    through a SOCKS proxy for lateral movement and hidden
    network enumeration during the pivot operation lab.

